<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:59:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Unitree 推出价值 574,000 美元的“mecha”机器人，可从 2 条腿“转变”为 4 条腿</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/unitree-debuts-us574000-mecha-robot-that-transforms-from-2-legs-to-4</link><description>在中国制造商大幅超越美国竞争对手之际，GD01 扩大了这家总部位于杭州的公司的产品组合。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unitree-debuts-us574000-mecha-robot-that-transforms-from-2-legs-to-4.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/unitree-debuts-us574000-mecha-robot-that-transforms-from-2-legs-to-4</guid></item><item><title>肝脏稳态和疾病中的库普弗细胞：从免疫哨兵到代谢看门人</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/kupffer-cells-in-liver-homeostasis-and-disease-from-immune-sentinels-to-metabolic-gatekeepers</link><description>这篇综述提供了库普弗细胞生物学的综合概述，从胚胎起源和空间组织到肝脏内的功能专业化。它强调库普弗细胞如何充当免疫哨兵，同时塑造代谢调节、组织修复、感染和癌症，并讨论新兴技术如何加深我们对其在生理和病理环境中的背景依赖性作用的理解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/kupffer-cells-in-liver-homeostasis-and-disease-from-immune-sentinels-to-metabolic-gatekeepers.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/kupffer-cells-in-liver-homeostasis-and-disease-from-immune-sentinels-to-metabolic-gatekeepers</guid></item><item><title>工程外泌体逆转小鼠睡眠剥夺脑损伤</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/engineered-exosomes-reverse-sleep-deprivation-brain-damage-in-mice</link><description>睡眠是一个重要的生理过程，可以让人类和其他动物恢复身心，同时巩固记忆、清除毒素和调节新陈代谢。过去的几项研究表明，长时间睡眠不足会引发炎症反应，并对人们的记忆、情绪、注意力和决策产生负面影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/engineered-exosomes-reverse-sleep-deprivation-brain-damage-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/engineered-exosomes-reverse-sleep-deprivation-brain-damage-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>雄性小鼠的类淋巴液流入与脑血容量呈负相关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glymphatic-influx-is-negatively-correlated-with-cerebral-blood-volume-in-male-mice</link><description>李等人。使用多模态 MRI 表明，脑血容量与六种大脑状态的类淋巴液流入呈负相关。较低的 CBV 与扩大的脑室外脑脊液空间有关，咖啡因在清醒小鼠中产生类似的模式，表明 CBV 作为补充脉动和血管舒缩的强直血管因子。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glymphatic-influx-is-negatively-correlated-with-cerebral-blood-volume-in-male-mice2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glymphatic-influx-is-negatively-correlated-with-cerebral-blood-volume-in-male-mice</guid></item><item><title>量子电路测试终于暴露了性能扭曲的原因</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-circuit-test-finally-exposes-what-has-been-warping-performance</link><description>量子计算机有一天可以解决对于经典计算机来说过于复杂的紧迫问题，例如对复杂的分子相互作用进行建模以简化药物发现和材料开发。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-circuit-test-finally-exposes-what-has-been-warping-performance3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 00:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-circuit-test-finally-exposes-what-has-been-warping-performance</guid></item><item><title>隐藏的细胞“信息途径”可能会改变癌症研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hidden-cell-message-route-could-shift-cancer-research</link><description>犹他大学亨斯曼癌症研究所的一个团队发现了一种以前未被认识的分子机制，细胞通过这种机制相互发送信号，这一见解可以帮助研究人员更好地了解癌症是如何形成的，并随着时间的推移，为新的治疗策略提供信息。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hidden-cell-message-route-could-shift-cancer-research.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 00:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hidden-cell-message-route-could-shift-cancer-research</guid></item><item><title>胶质母细胞瘤疫苗作为有前途的免疫疗法：挑战和现状</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glioblastoma-vaccines-as-promising-immune-therapeutics-challenges-and-current-status</link><description>胶质母细胞瘤（GBM）是最常见和最具侵袭性的恶性脑肿瘤。包括手术切除、放疗和化疗在内的标准治疗未能显着改善胶质母细胞瘤患者的预后。目前，基于疫苗、嵌合抗原受体T细胞、检查点抑制剂和溶瘤病毒疗法的免疫治疗方法在临床试验中显示出有希望的结果。不同免疫治疗方法的组合被证明是令人满意且有前途的。鉴于免疫治疗的挑战和胶质母细胞瘤的耐药性，这些肿瘤的治疗需要进一步努力。在这篇综述中，我们探讨了可能影响免疫治疗疗效且在临床试验中应考虑的障碍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glioblastoma-vaccines-as-promising-immune-therapeutics-challenges-and-current-status.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 00:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glioblastoma-vaccines-as-promising-immune-therapeutics-challenges-and-current-status</guid></item><item><title>第一个实时脑控听力设备</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/first-real-time-brain-controlled-hearing-device</link><description>研究人员展示了一种实时大脑控制的听力设备，可以根据听众的神经活动选择性地增强声音。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/first-real-time-brain-controlled-hearing-device.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 00:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/first-real-time-brain-controlled-hearing-device</guid></item><item><title>欧洲核子研究中心的物理学家可能即将发现“新物理学”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/physicists-may-be-on-the-verge-of-discovering-new-physics-at-cern</link><description>欧洲核子研究组织大型强子对撞机的物理学家发现了新的线索，表明某些粒子的衰变可能不会像标准模型预测的那样。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-may-be-on-the-verge-of-discovering-new-physics-at-cern.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 23:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/physicists-may-be-on-the-verge-of-discovering-new-physics-at-cern</guid></item><item><title>Qatsi 总监戈弗雷·雷吉奥：我们处于机器人状态！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/qatsi-director-godfrey-reggio-we-are-in-the-cyborg-state</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 23:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/qatsi-director-godfrey-reggio-we-are-in-the-cyborg-state</guid></item></channel></rss>